22 of 32 economists surveyed by Bloomberg News
expect a large and negative impact on financial markets should the government
postpone its plans of raising the sales tax from April next year.  NOTE 1: 2H = 2nd half of the year
NOTE 2: 2Q = 2nd quarter of the year
